---
<div id="consultation-modal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 hidden z-50">
  <div class="fixed inset-0 flex items-center justify-center p-2 sm:p-4">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl max-w-lg w-full p-4 sm:p-8 relative shadow-xl modal-content overflow-y-auto" style="max-height:90vh;">
      <!-- Close button -->
      <button
        onclick="document.getElementById('consultation-modal').classList.add('hidden')"
        class="absolute top-3 right-3 sm:top-4 sm:right-4 text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600"
        aria-label="Close"
      >
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
        </svg>
      </button>

      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold mb-6 text-gray-900 text-center">Get Expert Insurance Advice</h2>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-5 mb-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3 text-lg">Who is this meeting for?</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 mt-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 0L8 12.586 4.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l4 4a1 1 0 001.414 0l8-8a1 1 0 000-1.414z"/></svg></span> New residents needing to set up health insurance</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 mt-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 0L8 12.586 4.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l4 4a1 1 0 001.414 0l8-8a1 1 0 000-1.414z"/></svg></span> Current residents looking to optimize coverage and reduce premiums</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 mt-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 0L8 12.586 4.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l4 4a1 1 0 001.414 0l8-8a1 1 0 000-1.414z"/></svg></span> Anyone planning retirement with 3rd pillar options</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 mt-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 0L8 12.586 4.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l4 4a1 1 0 001.414 0l8-8a1 1 0 000-1.414z"/></svg></span> Families seeking life insurance protection</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 mt-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 0L8 12.586 4.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l4 4a1 1 0 001.414 0l8-8a1 1 0 000-1.414z"/></svg></span> Self-employed needing comprehensive insurance review</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-5 mb-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3 text-lg">What to expect:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 mt-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg></span> <span><b>30-60 minute consultation</b><br><span class="text-gray-500">Personal video call with our insurance expert</span></span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 mt-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/></svg></span> <span><b>Comprehensive Analysis</b><br><span class="text-gray-500">Review of all insurance needs (health, life, pension, etc.)</span></span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 mt-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg></span> <span><b>Tailored Solutions</b><br><span class="text-gray-500">Personalized recommendations for your situation</span></span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 mt-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" d="M9 12l2 2l4-4"/></svg></span> <span><b>Clear Next Steps</b><br><span class="text-gray-500">Written summary and action plan after the call</span></span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-4">
        <button
          data-cal-link="robertkolar/change-health-insurance"
          data-cal-namespace="expat-savvy"
          data-cal-config='{"layout":"month_view","theme":"light"}'
          type="button"
          class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-red-700 hover:bg-red-800 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect width="24" height="24" fill="none"/><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          Book Free Consultation
        </button>
        <button
          type="button"
          onclick="window.open('https://wa.me/41791552570', '_blank'); setTimeout(() => document.getElementById('consultation-modal').classList.add('hidden'), 500);"
          class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 mt-4 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-[#128C7E] hover:bg-[#075E54] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-[#075E54] transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
          </svg>
          Chat on WhatsApp
        </button>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 text-center mt-2">Our service is free - we're compensated by insurance providers when you choose to sign up through us.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  // Close modal when clicking outside
  document.getElementById('consultation-modal')?.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    if (e.target === e.currentTarget) {
      e.currentTarget.classList.add('hidden');
    }
  });
  // Function to show the modal globally
  window.showConsultationModal = function() {
    document.getElementById('consultation-modal')?.classList.remove('hidden');
    document.body.classList.add('modal-open');
  };
</script>

<style>
  .modal-content {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    max-height: 90vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .modal-content {
      margin: 0.5rem;
      max-height: 80vh;
      padding: 0.75rem !important;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .modal-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
    .modal-content h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .modal-content ul {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .modal-content button {
      font-size: 1rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    }
  }
  body.modal-open {
    overflow: hidden;
    position: fixed;
    width: 100%;
  }
</style>